   Help

Welcome to REGAFI. The Financial Firms Register.

   Last updated : 13 August 2019

   The register allows you to search for companies authorised to carry on
   banking activities, electronic money, financial services or payment
   services under the monetary and financial regulation.

Quick search

   When performing a search based on the name, please enter whether the
   full name or a keyword.

   Quick search

   Name : ____________________ Submit

Advanced search

   You are performing a multi-criteria search. The search returns relevant
   companies referenced in the register according to the criteria entered.
   The results will show one company or more, for each one you will be
   able to display additional information.
